SWASHBUCKLING
Type: Combat Action
See also: <help combat actions>

You are an aspiring duelist, on your way to mastering the rapier, and
have access to various specialized attacks in combat. Swashbucklers
find a strange luck in defeat, and seem to grow in skill with every
fumbled blow until they can overwhelm their opponent.

The honorable Aetarin warriors of Averath seem to produce the greatest 
swashbucklers.

Swashbuckling enables the following verbs:

1   : buckle (target)
1   : lunge (at target)
25  : parley (with target)
100 : harry (target)
200 : riposte
300 : skewer (target)
